org.apache.river.norm

Class NormServerInitializer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.river.norm.NormServerInitializer
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ActivatableNormServerImpl.Init

    class NormServerInitializer
extends Object
    NormServerInitializer creates the internal state of NormServerBaseImpl allowing many fields to be final after construction. This simplifies auditing of synchronization by reducing scope to mutable fields and references to mutable objects.
